annotationA: Ribosomal protein L36A, isoform A; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eL42 family
annotationB: Vig2, isoform B; It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of chromatin silencing; histone H3-K9 methylation; heterochromatin organization
